gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 120, Clippers 114
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Clippers, 120-114, and improve to 9-10 on the year. Stephen Curry led the Warriors with 26 points, seven rebounds, and eight assists as Klay Thompson (22 points, six rebounds) and Jonathan Kuminga (17 points, six rebounds, three assists) totaled 39 points. Kawhi Leonard led the Clippers with 23 points and seven rebounds as James Harden added 18 points and seven assists. The Clippers move to 8-10 on the season.
